        "subject": "LU-11371 lutf: set socklnd modparams using DLC",
        "message": "LU-11371 lutf: set socklnd modparams using DLC\n\nThis test script tests setting the socklnd\nmodparam - peer_credits using DLC.\n\nThis script configures lnet tcp with a\nnon-default peer_credits value using DLC.\nIt then checks if the value is set by\nrunning \"lnetctl net show -v\" and cleans\nup the configuration before returning.\n\nChange-Id: I9171a4d29fb7f549272c3299582c03248a2f1071\nTest-Parameters: trivial\nSigned-off-by: Sonia Sharma <sharmaso@whamcloud.com>\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/multi-rail"
    }
